Should be able to : 
1. Place orders to global warehouse
2. Receive orders from global warehouse
3. Cancel an order
4. Increase / Decrease store quantity
5. Increase display quantity
6. Be able to view entire inventory
7. Be able to view products
8. Show contents of a particular order and its status
9. Show all orders of given day
10. Show log of inventory transactions of given day
11. All product + quantity pairs corresponding to particular product on given day in orders
12. All product + quantity pairs corresponding to particular product on given day in inventory transactions